### ğŸ‘¨ğŸ‘©ğŸ‘§ğŸ‘¦ Additional ETH2 Community Guides

{% åµŒå…¥çš„ url="https://someresat.med.com/" %}

{% åµŒå…¥çš„ url="https://github.com/metanull-operator/eth2-ubuntu" %}

{% embed url="https://agstakingco.gitbook.io/eth-2-0-staking-guide-medalla/" %}

#### ç¡¬ä»¶Staking Guide [https://www.reddit.com/r/ethstaker/comments/j3mlup/a\_littly\_updated\_look\_hardware\_for\_staking/](https://www.reddit.com/r/ethstaker/comments/j3mlup/a_slightly_updated_look_at_hardware_for_staking/)

{% embed url="https://med.com/@RaymondDurk/how to stake-for-etherum-2-0-with-dappnode-231fa7689c0" %}

{% åµŒå…¥çš„ url="https://kb.beaconcha.in/" %}



